tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I recently had the pleasure of visiting Drm Sanneya's clinic for a root canal treatment, and I must say that the experience was nothing short of exceptional.
Firstly, I was impressed by her polite and sincere approach to patient care. She took the time to explain the procedure to me in detail, and her friendly demeanor immediately put me at ease. During the treatment, she displayed the utmost professionalism, skill, and attention to detail, which made me feel confident that I was in good hands.
However, what really sets her apart from other dentists is her commitment to following up with her patients during and after the treatment to ensure they are doing well. Not many doctors take the time to do that, and I really appreciate the personal touch she brings to your practice.
Overall, I highly recommend her services to anyone looking for a skilled and compassionate dentist. I thank her for the excellent care she provided, and I look forward to visiting her clinic again in the future.

review:
Dr. Sanneya is a saviour of my teeth, I was about to get one of my painful tooth extracted after advice from other doctor whom I was consulting earlier and was on antibiotics & pain killers and due to Covid, other doctor was unavailable and I walked in to Dr. Sanneya to get my tooth extracted. c)	NO antibiotics and almost no medicines

review:
In 2019 I had pain on one of my teeth. I visited a dentist. He took the x-ray, did the cleaning, filled the tooth, cut it and put a crown (cap) on it. I taught the root canal treatment is done and I would never have a pain on this tooth again. 2 months ago, I had an infection in the gum of the same tooth. Since, lockdown was going on, I couldn't visit any dentist. I took some medicines from the pharmacy. The infection was heald, but there was black marks on my gum. 2 weeks ago I visited Dr. Sanneya for consultation. She took an x-ray and unfortunately she informed me that the pervious root canal treatment was failed. So she recommended me to do retreatment ASAP. I started the retreatment of root canaling on my teeth with Dr. Sanneya and now as she said it is perfectly done and it will never cause any pain. 
Dr. Sanneya acts very professionally meanwhile friendly. Thanks
